only_totals: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.cgccpf) FROM proprietario p WHERE p.codproprietario  = (SELECT codproprietario  FROM proprietario p2  WHERE cgccpf  = p.cgccpf  ORDER BY COALESCE(dataatual, datainclusao) DESC LIMIT 1 );
initial_sync: SELECT prop.codproprietario, coalesce(prop.dataatual, prop.datainclusao) AS dataatual,prop.cgccpf,prop.liberado,prop.nome,prop.celular,prop.fone,prop.bloqueadoadm from proprietario prop WHERE prop.codproprietario = (select prop2.codproprietario from proprietario prop2 where prop.cgccpf = prop2.cgccpf order by coalesce(prop2.dataatual, prop2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) ORDER BY coalesce(prop.dataatual, prop.datainclusao), codproprietario;
daily_sync: SELECT coalesce(prop.dataatual, prop.datainclusao) AS dataatual, prop.cgccpf, prop.nome, prop.liberado, prop.bloqueadoadm, prop.obsbloq, mb.descricao AS MotivoBloqueio FROM proprietario prop LEFT OUTER JOIN motivobloqueio mb ON (prop.codmotivobloqueio = mb.codmotivobloqueio) WHERE coalesce(prop.dataatual, prop.datainclusao) >= '[$]' ORDER BY coalesce(prop.dataatual, prop.datainclusao) ASC;
working_table: SELECT prop.codproprietario, coalesce(prop.dataatual, prop.datainclusao) AS dataatual,prop.cgccpf,prop.liberado,prop.nome,prop.celular,prop.fone,prop.bloqueadoadm from proprietario prop WHERE prop.codproprietario = (select prop2.codproprietario from proprietario prop2 where prop.cgccpf = prop2.cgccpf order by coalesce(prop2.dataatual, prop2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) ORDER BY coalesce(prop.dataatual, prop.datainclusao) DESC LIMIT 1;
total_by_date: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT m.cgccpf) FROM proprietario m WHERE  coalesce(m.dataatual, m.datainclusao) >= '[$]';
total_by_status_0: select 'QTDproprietarios' as Tipo, 0 as Status,(SELECT count(prop.codproprietario)  FROM proprietario prop WHERE prop.codproprietario = (select prop2.codproprietario from proprietario prop2 where prop.cgccpf = prop2.cgccpf order by coalesce(prop2.dataatual, prop2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) AND prop.liberado = 'S' ) as QTD,current_date  as Data;
total_by_status_1: select  'QTDproprietarios' as Tipo, 1 as Status, (SELECT count(prop.codproprietario) FROM proprietario prop  WHERE prop.codproprietario = (select prop2.codproprietario from proprietario prop2 where prop.cgccpf = prop2.cgccpf  order by coalesce(prop2.dataatual, prop2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 )  AND prop.liberado = 'N' AND  prop.bloqueadoadm <> 'S' ) as QTD, current_date  as Data;
total_by_status_2: select  'QTDproprietarios' as Tipo, 2 as Status, (SELECT count(prop.codproprietario) FROM proprietario prop  WHERE prop.codproprietario = (select prop2.codproprietario from proprietario prop2 where prop.cgccpf = prop2.cgccpf  order by coalesce(prop2.dataatual, prop2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) AND prop.liberado = 'N' AND  prop.bloqueadoadm = 'S') as QTD, current_date  as data;
